A. LDR (Light Sensor)
Resistance changes according to light intensity.
Connected with a 10kΩ resistor as a voltage divider.
Arduino reads analog voltage using ADC.

Connection

LDR → 5V
Other terminal → A0
10kΩ → A0 to GND
B. DHT22 Sensor
Digital sensor for:
Temperature (°C)
Relative Humidity (%)

Connection

VCC → 5V
DATA → D2
GND → GND
C. HC-SR04 Ultrasonic Sensor
Sends ultrasonic pulse.
Measures return time of echo.
